Package: lektor
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Modern terminal-based text editor written in Rust
 Lektor is a powerful, modal terminal text editor written in Rust with
 features including:
  * Vim-like modal editing with normal, insert, visual, and command modes
  * Syntax highlighting for multiple programming languages
  * Git integration with status indicators and diff view
  * Multiple buffer management
  * Split panes for viewing multiple files
  * Session management for saving and restoring workspaces
  * Undo/redo with full history
  * Search and replace functionality
  * Customizable themes and configuration
  * File sidebar with directory tree navigation
